snippet.title: Marvel’s Spider-Man: The Heist – Just the Facts | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/marvels-spider-man/?emcid=or-1s-412983

Tune into Just the Facts with J. Jonah Jameson to learn more about the feline felon, Black Cat. 

Marvel’s Spider-Man: The Heist is available for download on the PlayStation®4 system now!

Marvel’s Spider-Man: The City That Never Sleeps is downloadable content for Marvel’s Spider-Man; may be sold separately. Marvel’s Spider-Man required to play associated downloadable content. Footage from Marvel’s Spider-Man: The Heist shown.
